        check on check boxes of recurring event that have same name in Monthview
        Parameters:

        number - the event's number of recurring event as first event =1, second event =2,.. Example: number="2". This means that second recurring event will be checked
        opt - the summary of recurring event instances of the same series that will be checked. Example:opt=3. This means that 3 recurring events will be checked
